{
  "path": "atlas/supported-unsupported/pipeline/out",
  "product": "atlas",
  "title": "$out Stage (Atlas Data Federation)",
  "description": "$out takes documents returned by the aggregation pipeline and writes\nthem to a specified collection. The $out operator must be the last\nstage in the aggregation pipeline. In Atlas Data Federation, you can use\n$out to write data from any one of the Storage Configuration federated database instance stores or multiple Storage Configuration\nfederated database instance stores when using federated queries\nto any one of the following:",
